ReferenceDocuments.description: This does not map directly to an SDTMIG variable. For the SDTM-based dataset, the SDTMIG variable PRSTAT is populated by mapping the value of the CDASH variable PRCSTAT "NOT COLLECTED" to "NOT DONE".
